title: Was the Corona virus funded by the spokesman for the United States House of Belosi?
subtitle: The blame game for responding to the krona virus is on, but some allegations are not always accurate.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: The President of the United States House of Representatives, Nancy Belusi, convened a funding package for the Corona virus so that the Democrats could run negative declarations about the Republicans that made the latter look bad.
